Quick Start
--------------------------
In order to start with the tutorial you require a minimal but working installation of ROCK. Just follow the installation procedure as described in the [step-by-step installation guide](startup/index.html)

To check if you are ready for your first tutorial open your console and enter 'which rock-create-lib' and verify that the command returns a full path to the 'rock-create-lib'-script. 
